This module is overriding TiViewController and TiRootViewController to fix the UIWebView crash bug, which happens in iOS 8.1 when using the <select> tag.

var webView = Ti.UI.createWebView({url: "http://www.w3schools.com/tags/tryit.asp?filename=tryhtml_select"});
$.index.add(webView);
$.index.open({modal: true});